  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">e truth . But just as a thing is signified by word, so it is by deed : and it is in this signification by deed that the outward worship of religion consists, as shown above ( II-II:81:07 ). Consequently, if anything false is signified by outward worship, this worship will be pernicious. Now thi</data>
