  <data key="d14">ann.concept-written-charm-observance-species-of-concept-superstitious-observance-st-ii-ii-q096-a004-resp</data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q096.a004.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">strong_textual_inference</data>
  <data key="d17">In every incantation or wearing of written words, two points seem to demand caution. The first is the thing said or written, because if it is connected with invocation of the demons it is clearly superstitiou</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_doctrinal</data>
</edge>
